QuickLook DDS Plugin
====================

This is a plugin for QuickLook on OSX 10.5 and later.
It allows Finder to display thumbnails and previews of DDS files.

Acknowledgements
----------------
Uses the SOIL library to decode DDS files - http://www.lonesock.net/soil.html
Nyx0uf for the idea of adding image dimensions to the preview title - http://www.cocoaintheshell.com/2012/02/quicklook-images-dimensions/

